<title type="html"><![CDATA[Praise Of Shaykh Albaani رحمه الله For Shaykh Waseeullah Abbaas حفظه الله]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=844&amp;p=888#p888"><![CDATA[
<strong><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal"><span style="color: #0000FF">Praise Of Shaykh Albaani رحمه الله For Shaykh Waseeullah Abbaas حفظه الله</span></span></strong><br /><br />Sheikh al-Muhaddith Muhammad Naasiruddeen al-Albany said:<br /><br />&quot;Verily, our companion Wasiullah Muhammad Abbaas has spoken in his annotation upon [the book] al-Fadaa'I&quot; with good speech regarding [this] Hadeeth.<br /><strong><em>[Silsilah Ahadeeth as-Saheehah no. 2295 Volume 5, Page 374]</em></strong><br /><br />In another place, the Shaykh says:<br />&quot;As narrated by the virtuous brother Wasiullah in his annotation upon 'al-Fadaa'il&quot;<br /><strong><em>[Silsilah Ahadeeth as-Saheehah no. 3318 Volume 8, Page 941]</em></strong><br /><br />He says in another place:<br />'I have mentioned a short while ago that [al~Imaam Muhammad lbn lsmaaeel ibn Ibraaheem ibn al-Mugheerah al-Ju'fee] al-Bukhaaree [d.255H] has narrated [this] Hadeeth in [his book] &quot;at-Taareekh&quot;, and the virtuous brother Wasiullah has preceded me in corroborating [the Hadeeth] upon the authority of al Bukhaaree in his annotation upon &quot;al-Fadaail.&quot;<br /><strong><em>[Silsilah Ahadeeth as-Saheehah no. 3437 Volume 8, Page 1290]</em></strong><br /><br />He says also:<br />I say: This is a grave error! [This error] has been elucidated by [al-Haafidh Jalaalud-Deen Abdur-Rahmaan as-Suyootee in [his book] al-La'aalee,&quot; and Ibn Iraaq in [his book] &quot;Tanzeeh ash-Sharee'ah&quot; and my companion, the one who has annotated upon [the book] FadaaiI as-Sahaabah, Wasiullah ibn Muhammad Abbaas, and other than them.<br /><strong><em>[Silsilah Ahadeeth ad-Da'eefah no. 5590 Volume 12, Page 187]</em></strong><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=56">Shehzad Sattar</a> — Fri Dec 16, 2016 11:24 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
